data.description:
AVAILABLE JANUARY 1, 2023. Located in the beautiful community of Olino at Mehana, you are going to love this 2 bedroom, 2.5 bath, 2 parking stall town home. Very well maintained home with an open floor plan and modern
designs throughout. The kitchen includes upgraded cabinets and all stainless steel appliances. Vinyl planks on the first floor and the stairs. Washer and dryer conveniently located upstairs where the bedrooms are. Keep cool and your electric bills down with the Split Air Conditioning Systems in the living room and bedrooms. Amenities include the Mehana community pool, a dog park, and walking/jogging paths. Centrally located in the heart of Kapolei, just a few minutes from Costco, Home Depot, the Kamakana Alii Mall, and a very short distance to the freeway. Rent includes water, sewer, and trash.

Water, sewer, trash included in rent. Tenant pays for electricity, cable, Internet. Renter's Insurance required.
